{
  "id": "267",
  "title": "Countries & Grammar",
  "subtitle": "Where are you from?",
  "theme": "playful",
  "colors": ["#FF9800", "#FFF3E0"],
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "block",
      "title": "1 Hello!",
      "text": "Hello! My name is Tom. I am from England. This is my friend Anna. She is from Russia."
    },
    {
      "type": "block",
      "title": "⭐ GRAMMAR 1: Positive (+)",
      "text": "Remember how to say who you are:\n\n• I am (I'm)\n• You are (You're)\n• He is (He's)\n• She is (She's)\n• It is (It's)\n\nExample: She is from Italy."
    },
    {
      "type": "vocab",
      "items": [
        { "en": "England", "ru": "Англия" },
        { "en": "China", "ru": "Китай" },
        { "en": "Italy", "ru": "Италия" },
        { "en": "Russia", "ru": "Россия" },
        { "en": "Spain", "ru": "Испания" },
        { "en": "Brazil", "ru": "Бразилия" },
        { "en": "USA", "ru": "США" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "block",
      "title": "⭐ GRAMMAR 2: Negative (-)",
      "text": "How to say NO:\n\n• I am NOT (I'm not)\n• You are NOT (You aren't)\n• He is NOT (He isn't)\n• She is NOT (She isn't)\n\nExample: He isn't from Spain."
    },
    {
      "type": "phrase",
      "items": [
        { "en": "Where are you from?", "ru": "Откуда ты?" },
        { "en": "I'm from Russia.", "ru": "Я из России." },
        { "en": "Is he from Italy?", "ru": "Он из Италии?" },
        { "en": "No, he isn't.", "ru": "Нет (не он)." },
        { "en": "Yes, she is.", "ru": "Да (она)." }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "block",
      "title": "⭐ GRAMMAR 3: Questions (?)",
      "text": "To ask a question, change the order:\n\n• Am I...?\n• Are you...?\n• Is he...?\n• Is she...?\n\nExample: Is she from Brazil? Yes, she is."
    },
    {
